        "title": "How to create an AST with a CAPTURE binding?",
        "body": "<p>I am interested in using the Eclipse JDT to create a <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/docs/books/jls/third_edition/html/conversions.html#5.1.10\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">CAPTURE<\/a> binding.<\/p>\n\n<p>I've read several capture conversion tutorials, but when I copy-paste sample code snippets, I can never find a capture conversion binding in the Abstract Syntax Tree (using the plugin ASTView for visualizing the AST).<\/p>\n\n<p>How can this be accomplished?<\/p>\n",
